Package: coheRence
Title: Coherence loss analysis based on OSM buildings and coherence maps
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Elias", "Andersch", , "Elias.andersch@stud-mail.uni-wurzburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to process Sentinel-1 coherence data in 
    conjunction with OpenStreetMap (OSM) building geometries. It 
    includes functions for automated clipping, data alignment, and 
    visualizing damage classes based on coherence loss.
